superdesign create-design-draft --project-id f184661d-4bc7-4e79-9273-6b67615d304b --title "Homepage — Norcineria Taccalite (Current)" -p 'Create a PIXEL-PERFECT reproduction of the current homepage. Match EXACTLY all element sizes, colors, spacing, fonts, border-radius, shadows and visual details from the provided source code — the reproduction must be indistinguishable from the original. Page structure top to bottom: (1) Sticky header (use the SiteHeader component, activeItem home). (2) Cinematic scroll intro stage (ScrollIntroSequence.tsx): a 400vh scroll-pinned full-viewport dark stage (#1c1512) with perspective 1200px; centered on it a large rounded-[28px] photo frame (54vh x 38vw) showing /images/home-hero-gastronomia.jpg; above it the eyebrow "NORCINERIA DAL 1946" in gold letterspaced uppercase and the "Taccalite" Playfair wordmark with per-character split reveal; two side frames (formaggi photo left at top 52% / left 15%, prosciutto photo right at top 18% / right 10%) that fly through z-space on scroll; two tiny background frames and gold blurred glow circles deep in the background. (3) Hero band on brown-950 with noise overlay: two-column grid, left column has gold uppercase eyebrow "Norcineria di famiglia · Ancona dal 1946", Playfair h1 "La tradizione norcina nel cuore delle Marche" (text-4xl to lg:text-6xl, cream), description paragraph, then two pill CTAs (gold "Scopri i nostri negozi", outlined cream "Prenota un tavolo"); right column a 4:3 rounded-2xl photo (home-hero-gastronomia.jpg) with a rotating 3D gold coin medallion floating at its bottom-right corner. (4) Section "I nostri negozi ad Ancona" on cream: eyebrow "Due negozi, una famiglia", Playfair h2, description, then 2-column grid of shop cards (photo top 4:3, gold-dark uppercase specialty, Playfair name, tagline, "Scopri il negozio →" link) for Taccalite Centro (Formaggi) and Taccalite Mercato del Piano (Carni & Salumi) using their real photos. (5) Dark brown-900 band: right column wide labelled image placeholder "Foto porchetta calda appena tagliata", left column light SectionHeading with eyebrow "La specialità della casa", h2 "La nostra porchetta", description, gold pill CTA "Scopri la porchetta →". (6) Section "I prodotti migliori" on cream: heading + 4-column grid of product cards, each with SQUARE labelled gradient placeholder image, category eyebrow, Playfair name, description, and pill "Disponibile in negozio · online a breve" (products: Porchetta artigianale, Ciauscolo IGP, Pecorino di fossa, Bistecca di razza marchigiana). (7) Blog preview band on cream-dark/60: heading "Dal nostro blog" with eyebrow "Novità" and right-aligned link "Vedi tutte le news →", then 3-column grid of blog cards (wide photo or placeholder, taupe date, Playfair title, excerpt) for the three posts in lib/data.ts. (8) Final section: 2-column grid of two rounded-2xl bordered white/50 cards — "Prenota un tavolo" with dark brown pill CTA "Prenota ora", and "Scheda fedeltà" with outlined pill CTA "Vai all'\''area personale". (9) Footer (use the SiteFooter component). Include Lenis-style smooth scrolling, scroll-reveal animations (fade + translateY, ease cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1)) and staggered card entrances exactly as the Reveal components define. Use the provided source code as the single source of truth.' --context-file .superdesign/design-system.md --context-file app/page.tsx --context-file components/ScrollIntroSequence.tsx --context-file components/Hero.tsx --context-file components/Header.tsx --context-file components/Footer.tsx --context-file components/SectionHeading.tsx --context-file components/ShopCard.tsx --context-file components/ProductCard.tsx --context-file components/BlogCard.tsx --context-file components/Photo.tsx --context-file components/ImagePlaceholder.tsx --context-file components/Reveal.tsx --context-file components/ui/button.tsx --context-file lib/data.ts --context-file lib/utils.ts --context-file app/globals.css --json
